#: release-9.5.xml:1154(para)
msgid ""
"Do not run the planner on the query contained in <literal>CREATE "
"MATERIALIZED VIEW</literal> or <literal>CREATE TABLE AS</literal> when "
"<literal>WITH NO DATA</literal> is specified (Michael Paquier, Tom Lane)"
