"Add system view <link linkend=\"view-pg-file-settings"
"\"><structname>pg_file_settings</structname></link> to show the contents of "
"the server's configuration files (Sawada Masahiko)"
msgstr ""
"Добавление системного представления <link linkend=\"view-pg-file-settings"
"\"><structname>pg_file_settings</structname></link>, показывающего "
"содержимое файлов конфигурации сервера (Савада Масахико)"

#. 2015-05-14 [a486e35] Peter ..: Add pg_settings.pending_restart column
#: release-9.5.xml:4416(para)
msgid ""
"Add <structname>pending_restart</structname> to the system view <link "
"linkend=\"view-pg-settings\"><structname>pg_settings</structname></link> to "
"indicate a change has been made but will not take effect until a database "
