"Вестстрате)"

#. 2014-10-18 [417f924] Bruce ..: interval:  tighten precision specification
#: release-9.5.xml:5127(para)
msgid ""
"Disallow non-SQL-standard syntax for <link linkend=\"datatype-interval-input"
